### Get Users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users


### Create User
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "name": "Manbat 1"
}

### Delete User
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/users?id=20f39a33-6d90-4b59-803d-3e6686c77958

### Modify User
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/users HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "id": "56c27001-7d5a-42a8-a309-7383dd0b9de4",
    "name": "Manbat from VS Code"
}

